reviewText: It was interesting but not fabulous.  I think folks who live on Long Island or study architecture may enjoy it more than I did.  There is another dvd I purchased from the History Channel on famous homes that I plan to watch next. Hopefully, that will be more exciting than this one. I still learned somethings from this video though. It's not a total loser.
A good survey of homes on old Gold Coast of LI. Used it in class to show students reading "The Great Gastby"
This is a good choice if you want to take a historical look back at the rich and famous of years gone by. Worth the price!
